arStrings.szText: It's my sons, Ordun and Khada. They used to work here with me in Ked Bardu, but then they got it in their heads to set up a new shop in Jirandai. You know how young men get when they're of age. Desperate to prove themselves.
If you are headed that way, would you mind checking up on them? The roads are so dangerous these days, and I haven't heard from them in so long.
